      <p>The format you choose matters more than the time you choose. Gummies have a 37% compliance advantage over powders for women specifically because they are convenient, portable, and require no mixing. For women starting creatine for the first time, gummy format dramatically improves the chances of building a sustainable daily habit.</p>
